購置七架單一全新型號的H175直升機，用作取代外號「超級美洲豹」的AS332直升機以及外號「海豚」的 EC155B1直升機，並於2018年7月起陸續付運。<br />\n<br />\n然而，今日其中一架H175於示威熱點低空盤旋，由香港國際機場 (HKG) 出發，先後到過上環、旺角警署附近、深水埗、荃灣、屯門、元朗、上水、大埔、沙田、黃大仙、將軍澳、港島東，經灣仔返回香港國際機場 (HKG) 。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">小編呼籲各位以及跟身邊朋友講，如果遇到直升機不尋常低飛/於市區內有行動，請拍下及私信給小編，讓小編可以立即知道即時消息以作求證飛行路線。</span></span></span>"},{"pid":"b996a7d1c4fa60133072db8dc4477c2cef3f55fa","tid":1519020,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:51:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"34193dbfa18c6811d4a8c5046e28830fc08eb595","tid":1519020,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T17:58:57.000Z","msg":"條路仲有排行，大家齊上齊落<br />\n要留命玩到去10月賀國慶<br />\n不被捕，不受傷"},{"pid":"3636ed9c512e80cf8cf62c353aa2e491bdd85bc4","tid":1519020,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:35:43.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"f5a387f30940fc4fca76a0f8c67135cd1fa5e11e","tid":1519020,"uid":10484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:37:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"58346365d3460e3f95b162303317fbd22e102335","tid":1519020,"uid":64385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:41:27.000Z","msg":"早幾星期有吹風傳過空降速龍<br />\n手足記得留心周圍環境<br />\n<br />\n光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"55ede242fdf89ff8b7c86321cc75cc61eaaa50c1","tid":1519020,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T18:41:39.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"f113ad4425be02bfc1dcb4b5cfac0a2ee759b6bc","tid":1519020,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:56:34.000Z","msg":"P"},{"pid":"2846d2c6b6910f46b41d3b8f5079c14d2ec46bd4","tid":1519020,"uid":68125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T05:29:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2697b4ffcad914a504b3f77bc1cd55e8b7f36443","tid":1519020,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl